text: Valentine Dumont (born 2 July 2000) is a Belgian swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. In 2017, she won the silver medal in the girls' 200 metre freestyle at the 2017 European Junior Swimming Championships held in Netanya, Israel. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Belgian female freestyle swimmers
